<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:13:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>瑞银表示全球对冲基金追逐港股反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-global-hedge-funds-chase-hong-kong-stocks-rally-ubs-says-2024-05-03/</link><description>瑞银集团在一份报告中表示，采用股票多空策略的全球对冲基金越来越看好中国，其购买香港上市股票的大幅增加就证明了这一点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:48:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-global-hedge-funds-chase-hong-kong-stocks-rally-ubs-says-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市因科技股上涨而上涨；日元扩大涨势以限制疯狂的一周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-03/</link><description>苹果公司创纪录的 1100 亿美元股票回购计划提振了科技板块，周五亚洲股市上涨，而日元则远离近期 34 年来的低点，结束了东京疑似干预的动荡一周。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:19:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>导弹防御在海湾和乌克兰的成功加剧了全球采购系统的紧迫性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/missile-defence-successes-gulf-ukraine-fuel-global-urgency-acquire-systems-2024-05-03/</link><description>专家表示，弹道导弹防御系统在以色列、红海和乌克兰首次面临复杂、高风险的战斗场景时取得成功，将鼓励全球军队投资昂贵的系统，并加剧导弹军备竞赛。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 02:02:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/missile-defence-successes-gulf-ukraine-fuel-global-urgency-acquire-systems-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称中国飞机越过中线，中国进行着陆演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-14-chinese-military-planes-crossed-straits-median-line-2024-05-03/</link><description>台湾国防部周五表示，发现中国军机再次侵入敏感的台湾海峡，中国报道称其海军已使用登陆艇进行了战斗演习。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 01:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-14-chinese-military-planes-crossed-straits-median-line-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>日元有望创一年多以来最佳单周表现；美元等待美国就业数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-poised-best-week-over-year-dollar-waits-us-jobs-data-2024-05-03/</link><description>周五，日元将迎来一年多来表现最好的一周，这得益于东京本周疑似进行干预，将日元拉离34年来的低点，这也让美元普遍处于不利地位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:26:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-poised-best-week-over-year-dollar-waits-us-jobs-data-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>法拉利推出两款全新 V12 赛车，吸引传统消费者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ferrari-appeals-traditional-base-with-two-new-v12-cars-2024-05-03/</link><description>豪华跑车制造商法拉利推出了两款新车型：12Cilindri 和 12Cilindri Spider，吸引了其最强大的轰鸣汽油发动机的爱好者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 00:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ferrari-appeals-traditional-base-with-two-new-v12-cars-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰外长称中国关系复杂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-foreign-minister-calls-china-relationship-complex-2024-05-02/</link><description>新西兰外交部长周五称该国与中国的关系“复杂”，并指出台湾海峡两岸的强硬言论、香港的侵犯人权行为以及“加强对太平洋安全领域的参与”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:57:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-foreign-minister-calls-china-relationship-complex-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场喜爱美联储，日元喜爱日本央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-02/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 21:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>FCC表示，美国电信公司需要更多资金来移除中国设备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/many-us-telecom-firms-need-more-funding-replace-huawei-zte-equipment-fcc-says-2024-05-02/</link><description>美国联邦通信委员会 (FCC) 周四表示，在获得联邦支持的美国电信公司中，近 40% 需要额外的政府资金，以将中国电信公司华为和中兴制造的设备从美国无线网络中移除，以应对安全风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 18:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/many-us-telecom-firms-need-more-funding-replace-huawei-zte-equipment-fcc-says-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>塞尔维亚议会批准联合政府</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbian-parliament-approves-coalition-government-2024-05-02/</link><description>塞尔维亚议会周四批准了一个联合政府，新当选的总理米洛斯·武切维奇将其描述为“连续性政府”，它将带领巴尔干国家应对地缘政治挑战以及与科索沃的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 17:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbian-parliament-approves-coalition-government-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称有关其与朝鲜军事关系的说法不准确</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-calls-claim-about-its-alleged-military-ties-with-north-korea-inaccurate-2024-05-02/</link><description>俄罗斯周四表示，西方关于其与朝鲜进行军事合作的说法是不准确的，并表示其与平壤的关系既不针对第三国，也不威胁该地区的安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 15:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-calls-claim-about-its-alleged-military-ties-with-north-korea-inaccurate-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国孖士打律师事务所将退出香港合伙企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-law-firm-mayer-brown-split-hong-kong-partnership-2024-05-02/</link><description>美国孖士打律师事务所周四表示，由于许多国际律师事务所重新考虑或减少在中国的业务，该公司计划从目前的香港业务中分离出来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 14:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/us-law-firm-mayer-brown-split-hong-kong-partnership-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>习近平的欧洲之行可能暴露西方对中国战略的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/xis-trip-europe-may-lay-bare-wests-divisions-over-china-strategy-2024-05-02/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平下周将五年来首次访问欧洲，这次访问可能会暴露欧洲在与北京的贸易问题上的分歧，以及欧洲大陆如何将自己定位为美国和中国之间的一极。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/xis-trip-europe-may-lay-bare-wests-divisions-over-china-strategy-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>五一假期中国旅游激增，但消费者仍保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-travel-surges-may-holiday-consumers-remain-wary-2024-05-02/</link><description>周三，即重大公众假期的第一天，中国各地的铁路和汽车出行激增，因为消费者仍然专注于在充满挑战的经济中降低开支。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-travel-surges-may-holiday-consumers-remain-wary-2024-05-02/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能带动中国智能手机市场反弹，高通股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</link><description>高通公司股价周四上涨约 10% 至两年多高点，此前这家专注于智能手机的芯片制造商表示，在经历了多年的低迷之后，人工智能推动的需求出现反弹，尤其是在中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/qualcomm-jumps-ai-sparks-rebound-chinese-smartphone-market-2024-05-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>